---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const CAL_URL = "https://cal.com/isabella-rondon-jrkvbh/30min";
---

<Layout
  title="Custom AI Agent Development for Business — Case Study"
  description="Custom AI agent development for a car dealership — 24/7 customer service, silent lead qualification, appointment scheduling, and demand capture. Built on n8n with OpenAI and Anthropic APIs."
>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://isabellarondon.com/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Case Studies", "item": "https://isabellarondon.com/case-studies/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "AI Agent Development", "item": "https://isabellarondon.com/case-studies/ai-sales-agent-car-dealership/" }
    ]
  })} />

  <!-- CASE STUDY HEADER -->
  <header class="cs-header">
    <div class="cs-header-inner">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="cs-back">← Case Studies</a>
      <div class="cs-tag">AI Agent Development</div>
      <h1 class="cs-headline">
        Most people talk about what an AI agent could do.<br>
        <span style="color: var(--accent-light);">Here's how this one talks to customers.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="cs-subheadline">I built a fully functional AI sales agent for a car dealership — trained on their real business rules, integrated with their actual systems, and ready to deploy. Not a template. A working agent.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- STATS BAR -->
  <div class="cs-stats-bar">
    <div class="cs-stat-item">
      <div class="cs-stat-value">24/7</div>
      <div class="cs-stat-label">availability — no staff needed</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="cs-stat-item">
      <div class="cs-stat-value">5</div>
      <div class="cs-stat-label">automated workflows</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat-divider"></div>
    <div class="cs-stat-item">
      <div class="cs-stat-value">100%</div>
      <div class="cs-stat-label">built on this dealership's real business rules</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RESULTS TABLE — proof-first -->
  <section class="cs-results-summary">
    <div class="cs-results-summary-label">Without the Agent vs. With the Agent</div>
    <div class="cs-results-table">
      <div class="cs-results-header">
        <span>Situation</span>
        <span>Without the Agent</span>
        <span>With the Agent</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-results-row">
        <span class="cs-metric"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg></span>After-hours leads</span>
        <span>Lost — no coverage</span>
        <span class="after">Handled immediately, 24/7</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-results-row">
        <span class="cs-metric"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg></span>Inventory &amp; pricing questions</span>
        <span>Wait for staff availability</span>
        <span class="after">Answered in real time</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-results-row">
        <span class="cs-metric"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg></span>Car or accessory not in stock</span>
        <span>Lead disappears</span>
        <span class="after">Logged as structured demand data</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-results-row">
        <span class="cs-metric"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg></span>Appointment booking</span>
        <span>Manual — human handoff required</span>
        <span class="after">Booked directly into database</span>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-results-row">
        <span class="cs-metric"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="22 3 2 3 10 12.46 10 19 14 21 14 12.46 22 3"/></svg></span>Lead qualification</span>
        <span>Sales team time</span>
        <span class="after">Silent and automatic</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TWO-COLUMN: NARRATIVE LEFT · STACK SIDEBAR RIGHT -->
  <div class="cs-two-col">

    <!-- LEFT: narrative -->
    <div class="cs-two-col-main">

      <section class="cs-section">
        <h2 class="cs-section-title">The Problem</h2>
        <div class="cs-body">
          <p>A car dealership's sales cycle doesn't stop at 6pm. Leads come in on weekends, after hours, and during peak seasons when the floor team is overwhelmed. Every unanswered message is a lost opportunity — and hiring more staff to cover every time window doesn't scale.</p>
          <p>Beyond availability, there was a subtler problem: no visibility into what customers actually wanted when a specific car wasn't in stock. That demand was disappearing into thin air instead of informing inventory and sales strategy.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cs-section">
        <h2 class="cs-section-title">What the Agent Does</h2>
        <div class="cs-body">
          <p>I designed and built a production-ready AI agent from scratch — trained on the dealership's real business rules, inventory logic, and customer service policies.</p>

          <div class="cs-decisions">
            <div class="cs-decision-title">Five workflows, fully automated</div>
            <div class="cs-decision-item">
              <div class="cs-decision-name"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg></span>Customer service</div>
              <div class="cs-decision-desc">Answers questions about location, hours, delivery, and inventory in natural, accurate language.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-decision-item">
              <div class="cs-decision-name"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg></span>Financing offers</div>
              <div class="cs-decision-desc">If a customer's budget doesn't cover a vehicle, the agent proactively presents financing options and walks them through the process.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-decision-item">
              <div class="cs-decision-name"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg></span>Appointment scheduling</div>
              <div class="cs-decision-desc">Books showroom visits directly into a database — no human handoff required.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-decision-item">
              <div class="cs-decision-name"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg></span>Silent demand capture</div>
              <div class="cs-decision-desc">When a customer asks for a car or accessory that isn't in stock, the agent logs the request silently. Every unavailable inquiry becomes a demand signal for inventory planning.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cs-decision-item">
              <div class="cs-decision-name"><span class="cs-row-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="15 14 20 9 15 4"/><path d="M4 20v-7a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h12"/></svg></span>Smart handoff</div>
              <div class="cs-decision-desc">When a conversation reaches a decision point that requires a human, the agent transfers cleanly with full context.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="cs-section">
        <h2 class="cs-section-title">See It For Yourself</h2>
        <div class="cs-body">
          <div class="cs-demo-tag"><span class="dot"></span> Real conversation</div>
          <p>Here's a real exchange handled end-to-end by the agent — no human involved at any point.</p>

          <div class="cs-demo-wrap">

            <ul class="cs-demo-points">
              <li><strong>Inventory check</strong> — answers pricing and availability instantly, in natural language</li>
              <li><strong>Appointment booking</strong> — schedules the showroom visit directly into the database</li>
              <li><strong>Silent demand capture</strong> — logs the request for a red RAV4 for the inventory team, with no extra step for the customer</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="phone-stage">
              <div class="phone-glow"></div>
              <div class="phone-frame">
                <div class="phone-notch"></div>
                <div class="phone-screen">

                  <div class="chat-header">
                    <div class="chat-avatar">AI</div>
                    <div class="chat-id">
                      <div class="chat-name">Dealership Assistant</div>
                      <div class="chat-status"><span class="dot"></span> online</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="chat-body">
                    <div class="bubble-row in">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-in">Hi! Do you have any Toyota RAV4 in stock under $30k?</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:41 AM</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bubble-row out">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-out">Yes — a 2022 RAV4 LE, $28,500, 31k miles. Want to see it in person?</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:41 AM</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bubble-row in">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-in">Sure, this Saturday at 11am?</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:42 AM</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bubble-row out">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-out">You're booked for Saturday, 11:00 AM. We'll send a reminder the day before.</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:42 AM</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bubble-row in">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-in">One more thing — do you have it in red?</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:43 AM</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bubble-row out">
                      <div class="bubble bubble-out">Not in red at the moment — but I can let you know as soon as one's available. Anything else I can help with?</div>
                      <div class="bubble-time">9:43 AM</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="chat-input-bar">
                    <div class="chat-input-fake"></div>
                    <div class="chat-send"></div>
                  </div>

                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: sticky sidebar -->
    <div class="cs-two-col-sidebar">

      <div class="cs-sidebar-card">
        <div class="cs-sidebar-label">Stack Used</div>
        <div class="cs-sidebar-tags">
          <span>n8n</span>
          <span>OpenAI API</span>
          <span>Anthropic API</span>
          <span>Database integrations</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cs-sidebar-cta">
        <p>Curious what an agent like this could handle for your business?</p>
        <a href={CAL_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener">See if this fits your team →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- CTA BLOCK -->
  <div class="cs-cta-block">
    <div class="cs-cta-inner">
      <div class="cs-cta-left">
        <h2 class="cs-cta-headline">Want an agent built for your business rules, not a generic chatbot?</h2>
        <p class="cs-cta-sub">Every AI agent I build starts with your workflows, your edge cases, and your customer language — not a template. The result is an agent your team can trust to run without supervision.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-cta-right">
        <a href={CAL_URL} class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Book a Discovery Call &nbsp;→</a>
        <span class="cta-note">No commitment. 30 minutes.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
